These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding, cricket, soccer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, april, august
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, bartender, fisherman, mechanic
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the fisherman is in an even position##4
 9. the paramedic is between the mechanic and the fan of techno##2
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the mechanic##1
11. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Sport          | cricket  | rugby    | soccer    | skateboarding   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| Birthday   | january | june | august    | april |
| Job           | bartender | mechanic       | paramedic | fisherman     |

