.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, scientific, thriller, comedy
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, yellow, aquamarine, lavender
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, project-manager, fisherman, lawyer
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the project-manager##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is the person who likes light-blue##1
 5. the lawyer is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the engineer##3
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
11. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | family  | scientific    | thriller     | comedy       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Color   | aquamarine | light-blue   | yellow   | lavender    |
| Job         | fisherman | lawyer  | engineer | project-manager   |

