.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, ivory, brown, lilac
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, swisher, tiparillo, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, punk, blues, gospel
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 2. the fan of punk is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 3. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is the bolivar-smoker##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the fan of gospel##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the person who likes brown is on the left of the fan of funk##1
10. the owner of the dog is the person who likes brown##1
11. the person who likes amber is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Color      | amber | brown   | lilac    | ivory      |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | fonseca | swisher | bolivar     |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | gospel   | funk   | blues |
| Pet           | mouse         | dog       | hedgehog  | goat       |

