.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
4 different games are played: rat, mah-jongg, go, billiard
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, goat, pony
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, december, august
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person playing rat##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the person playing rat is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 4. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the person playing billiard##1
12. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Game       | mah-jongg        | billiard | rat    | go       |
| Pet      | pony | rat    | goat  | lizard |
| Birthday      | june  | december  | july | august    |

