There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, disco, soul, funk
 1. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the fan of r&b and the blend-smoker##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 4. the librarian is the dannemann-smoker##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
 7. the montecristo-smoker is the bartender##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the librarian##1
 9. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Cigar    | prince    | blend      | dannemann          | montecristo    |
| Beverage   | sprite | soy-milk       | hot-chocolate | lemonade |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | funk | soul        | r&b   |

