City: hamburg, venice, berlin, marseilles
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, turquise, brown, white
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, daisy, marigold, sunflower
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 5. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who likes white is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who likes turquise##2
 7. the person who likes brown is the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | iced-tea    | 7up       | tea       |
| City          | marseilles    | berlin | venice | hamburg     |
| Color   | lavender | brown        | white    | turquise   |
| Flower   | begonia  | marigold      | sunflower    | daisy |

