 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
10. the egyptian is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
