The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, snowboarding, water-polo
 1. the person who likes black is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
 3. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
