 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City      | liverpool   | boston   | colone     | san-francisco   |
| Birthday   | march  | august       | october | april |
| Flower           | bellflower     | daffodil   | lily     | dahlia     |
| Sport         | volleyball | ice-hockey | handball   | cycling |

