.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, indie, disco, rock
City: nizza, liverpool, rome, hannover
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, yellow, black, chestnut
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
10. the person who likes black is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person traveling to nizza is the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Music-Genre      | disco       | indie | electronic        | rock        |
| City         | hannover | rome       | nizza | liverpool |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| Color         | yellow     | black    | chestnut | light-blue   |

