.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, swisher, blend, cain
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, polish
4 different games are played: go, chess, bridge, domino
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, security-guard, project-manager, manager
 1. the cain-smoker is the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person playing bridge is between the australian and the polish##2
 3. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person playing go is on the right of the manager##1
 6. the swisher-smoker is the person playing chess##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
 8. the polish is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
10. the australian is in an even position##4
11. the australian is on the far right##1
12. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | swisher      | tiparillo | cain     | blend        |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | french     | australian |
| Game         | chess    | go | bridge      | domino |
| Job     | manager | security-guard     | project-manager | teacher       |

 